compare phytosterols, fatty acids, tocopherols, and polyphenols contents of dietary and cosmetic argan
oil (AO), olive oil (OO; Tunisia, Morocco and Spain), silybummarianumseed oils (SMSO; Zaghouane,
Bizerte, Sousse), nigella seed oil (NSO) and colza oil (CO), using analytical methods. The antioxidant
potential of the oils was evaluated with KRL test. Oils had high C18:2 contents, with highest amounts
